    <p><strong>Elevator pitch:</strong> A Just Eat clone for lunchtime without the delivery.</p>

    <p><strong>Client: </strong>Local office workers that want a change from the usual Tesco mealdeal but don’t want to spend their lunch hour visiting lots of different places.</p>
    
    <p><strong>Features </strong></p>
		<p>For the Visitor</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Search for closest by postcode.</li>
      <li>A Randomiser that presents a potential lunch choice.</li>
			<li>Search by category of food.  </li>
		</ul>
		
		<p>For the Visitor</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Items can be selected as ‘Specials’ and are indicated at the top of the menu</li>
		</ul>
